          { question: "How much are the Toulouse — Millau tolls?", answer: "Tolls include the A68 (~€7) and the Millau Viaduct (~€10 in summer). Total approximately €17, included in the TaxiNeo fixed price." },
          { question: "Can I paddle the Tarn Gorges in one day from Millau?", answer: "Yes, by canoe-kayak from La Malene to Hauterives (about 5h paddling, pristine canyon experience). Your driver can drop you off and pick you up." },
          { question: "Is there a train to Millau?", answer: "No, Millau station is closed to passenger traffic. The bus is very slow (3h30). The taxi is the most practical and fastest solution from Toulouse." }
